}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 "WORSHIP NOTES" - }{\plain \fs24 \f8 With the start of the Fall Season, "Modern" (contemporary) Worship will once again \softline
occasionally be a part of our 11:00 AM worship service schedule. During the Fall months, Modern Worship will \softline
occur on November 4 & 18.  Also, starting on September 30, we will introduce Setting Four of the Liturgy from \softline
Lutheran Service Book (LSB page 208 ff).  We'll use Setting Four during the months of October and November \softline
prior to returning to Setting One for Advent beginning December 2.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Men's Prayer Breakfast:}{\plain \fs24 \f8  Men of the congregation are invited to join other Living Savior men for breakfast, prayer \softline
and Bible study every 2nd and 4th Saturday from 7 - 8:30am. Our new study is on Martin Luther: Gospel and Law. \softline
Questions?  Contact Paul Gross.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
