}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Operation Christmas Child (OCC) }{\plain \fs24 \f8 brings joy and hope to children in desperate situations around the world \softline
through gift-filled shoeboxes and the Good News of God's love.  OCC has delivered over 135 million shoeboxes \softline
to children affected by war, poverty, natural disasters, and other crises in more than 150 countries and territories. \softline
Bring your filled shoe boxes to church by Sunday, November 18th and they will be delivered to a local collection \softline
center. }{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Brochures and boxes are available in the walkway!}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
